The '''Faljozic''' [[Kajidic/Legends|kajidic]] was a [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] kajidic located on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], which controlled most exports from Tatooine before [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba's]] rise to power. Like four other Hutt kajidics, the Faljozic controlled nearly one-fifth of Tatooine's criminal activities before Jabba seized control of planetary operations.

